title: Circle Internet Aces Its First Earnings Test. The Stock Rises.
snippet: But Circle faced another market test: its first earnings report as a public company. Circle, which has a partnership with crypto investing leader Coinbase, reported its results for the second quarter on Tuesday. Sales were $658 million, up 53% from a year ago and ahead of analysts' forecasts of $646 million.

title: Stock-Market Debut of Bullish Is a Big Test of IPO Pricing
snippet: The initial public offering for Bullish, a cryptocurrency exchange focused on institutional investors, will be a test of its CEO, Tom Farley. Farley guided some of the buzziest IPOs when he was president of the New York Stock Exchange.

title: Wall St Week Ahead Inflation data to test stocks as some investors brace for rally to pause
